# WakeUp App Context

## Project Overview
WakeUp is a science-backed morning routine app that helps users start their day with cognitive exercises and day preparation.

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: React Native (Expo) with TypeScript
- Backend: Node.js + Express + TypeScript (coming later)
- State: Zustand for global state management
- Navigation: React Navigation v6

## Key Features
### Free Tier
- Smart alarm with cognitive unlock
- 5 exercise types: Math, Memory, Breathing, Word, Pattern
- Basic day preview (weather + calendar)
- Progress tracking with streaks

### Premium Tier ($4.99/month)
- Advanced exercise library
- Full calendar integration
- Detailed analytics
- Custom routine builder

